title: Art Institute of Chicago Magic Pencil Set
description:
This set of 3 of magic pencils feature multi-color cores. Each swipe of the pencil reveals a surprising color and pattern combination. Extra-wide barrel is perfect for artists of all ages.

  • 3 pencils.
  • Pencil dimension: 7 in.
  • Lead of each pencil contains 3 distinct colors.
  • Plastic Art Institute of Chicago slipcover.
